---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <div class="mb-10 text-center">
    <h1 class="gradient-text text-4xl font-bold">About</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="post-content mx-auto max-w-2xl">
    <p>
      Hey there! I'm <strong>Diego</strong>, the person behind <strong>tag.dev</strong>.
      I build things for the web and write about what I learn along the way.
    </p>

    <p>
      This blog is my personal space to share thoughts on web development,
      programming languages, tools, and the occasional random experiment.
      Expect posts about Astro, Vue, Tailwind CSS, and whatever else I'm
      tinkering with at the moment.
    </p>

    <h2>Get in touch</h2>

    <p>
      Feel free to reach out — I'm always happy to chat about code,
      ideas, or collaboration.
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li><strong>GitHub</strong> — github.com/diegodiaz</li>
      <li><strong>Email</strong> — diego@tag.dev</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Layout>
